Requirements
------------
	Python 2.2 or greater
	GCC
	LibXML requirements and associated Python bindings
	XML Security Library version >= 1.2.0

To build
--------
	Edit setup.py to set correct values in define_macros, include_dirs,
	library_dirs and libraries

	./setup.py build

To clean
--------
	./setup.py clean -a

To install
----------
	./setup.py install
This step requires root access.
